snippet.title: Timbertales - Official Trailer [HD 1080P] (Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Timbertales - Official Trailer in HD 1080P contains also a lot of gameplay action.

Buy it now on:
https://timbertales.net/
https://store.steampowered.com/app/673480/Timbertales/
https://ruffiely.itch.io/timbertales

I updated so much since the first trailer was released, so I thought it was time to create a new one. I am absolutely not very expertise in making trailers, but hell yeah I think it is one of my best :)

Timbertales is a turn based strategy game.

You need a specific Godot topic coverd? Consider to become a Patreon and request your own tutorial video!

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/rainware

Thank you for watching and supporting my channel!
